column4: Text
NSLOCTEXT("[05E61EAF43335DD037F8E3A956D5F63F]", "CB91C651491C985150E92183E0EA8E30", "What is it?!")
NSLOCTEXT("[05E61EAF43335DD037F8E3A956D5F63F]", "A2C57AC94FA6A182DDD421942DFCC619", "Oh, welcome back, Hagurumon!")
NSLOCTEXT("[05E61EAF43335DD037F8E3A956D5F63F]", "989388F548D2808888BF3984CBE3F4EC", "Hagurumon?!")
NSLOCTEXT("[05E61EAF43335DD037F8E3A956D5F63F]", "024FD0DC4DEBE19A96F001B697BE1DF6", "What\'s going on?!")
NSLOCTEXT("[05E61EAF43335DD037F8E3A956D5F63F]", "A995FE9441BF305C7F5D92A3278B7A6D", "It\'s an old tale. A bad guy came from far away to this island.")
NSLOCTEXT("[05E61EAF43335DD037F8E3A956D5F63F]", "26D36A1F4C8590926EF9CE91A63F813F", "The bad guys told Digimon: This island is ours.")
NSLOCTEXT("[05E61EAF43335DD037F8E3A956D5F63F]", "B900E69C43E302DBE6E423962DB97D4A", "Digimon told them: That\'s not true. This island is for everybody.")
NSLOCTEXT("[05E61EAF43335DD037F8E3A956D5F63F]", "63F407924D4350DAEAE43CAE0F46C9C8", "Because Digimons unified and challenged the bad guys, the bad guys were taught a lesson.")
NSLOCTEXT("[05E61EAF43335DD037F8E3A956D5F63F]", "25923C1744B9834BB8B6D9B5D937B845", "But the bad guys said: Wait, we\'ll get you later. ...and they disappeared.")
NSLOCTEXT("[05E61EAF43335DD037F8E3A956D5F63F]", "E3A422F24B51DB68A58AA9979370CB1B", "It\'s an old tale.")
NSLOCTEXT("[05E61EAF43335DD037F8E3A956D5F63F]", "577B3D434CD5EF5DCDE5109FDC26A2DA", "Hmmm, I feel joyous... Oh, wait up.")
NSLOCTEXT("[05E61EAF43335DD037F8E3A956D5F63F]", "A2AC216B49ADED3C223A59BD4FE0A2FD", "That story from the song is an old tale of this island, isn\'t it?")
NSLOCTEXT("[05E61EAF43335DD037F8E3A956D5F63F]", "6E65EA3041C66C5F76BB16A635AE591C", "About the Digimon defeating the bad guys...")
NSLOCTEXT("[05E61EAF43335DD037F8E3A956D5F63F]", "634C77C34EDD8E8D7A4C40B80FED6BF1", "Hmmm, I wonder who the bad guys were in the story?")
NSLOCTEXT("[05E61EAF43335DD037F8E3A956D5F63F]", "220F0FE14D45C2E519D102884A88C065", "Thanks for helping me. This is to show my gratitude.")
NSLOCTEXT("[05E61EAF43335DD037F8E3A956D5F63F]", "37D22B4C4C0A09354D767B947706A07F", "Monzaemon\'s Stuffed Animal joins the city!")
NSLOCTEXT("[05E61EAF43335DD037F8E3A956D5F63F]", "CCEC7085409C5A49540698A17DEA5419", "Wait, didn\'t WaruMonzaemon drop something?")
NSLOCTEXT("[05E61EAF43335DD037F8E3A956D5F63F]", "94089BEA41A6D69DA3CB1697E14E804A", "Good luck! It\'s the house next door!")
INVTEXT("......")
NSLOCTEXT("[05E61EAF43335DD037F8E3A956D5F63F]", "DCB093A74372A5E185B6F78BD932C978", "Are we going to listen to the chorus again?")
NSLOCTEXT("[05E61EAF43335DD037F8E3A956D5F63F]", "CCF804D44CA223276D57159838E51FE6", "Oh, Monzaemon! You\'re back alive!")
NSLOCTEXT("[05E61EAF43335DD037F8E3A956D5F63F]", "1EBB23204AA1DEABAE0E7284E4645C76", "Wow, what is it?")
NSLOCTEXT("[05E61EAF43335DD037F8E3A956D5F63F]", "2F5A81464414A9207764D49BA0E7D92C", "Go fight WaruMonzaemon! Quickly, everybody get moving! Quick, quick!")
NSLOCTEXT("[05E61EAF43335DD037F8E3A956D5F63F]", "F2AA84264568B5B552A499B7A014DB69", "Wait...wait! He\'s not the Monzaemon you all know.")
NSLOCTEXT("[05E61EAF43335DD037F8E3A956D5F63F]", "77D776F340BE2FBB2005C09D932FDCC0", "Huh? What do you mean? But he is a Monzaemon, right?")
NSLOCTEXT("[05E61EAF43335DD037F8E3A956D5F63F]", "F3E9D9F44AD63EA7D9315FA7EFB05E9A", "Yeah, it\'s true that he\'s a Monzaemon.")
NSLOCTEXT("[05E61EAF43335DD037F8E3A956D5F63F]", "DB90FE0448FD4B22416BF88A695F15F2", "A bad guy called WaruMonzaemon kidnapped our friend.")
NSLOCTEXT("[05E61EAF43335DD037F8E3A956D5F63F]", "B3D1D14B4AD560D216FCBD94BCCF0CB7", "I think the only one who can defeat him is Monzaemon!")
NSLOCTEXT("[05E61EAF43335DD037F8E3A956D5F63F]", "5B0D24814ADF0665F34F4CA4F09625F9", "Hmm, then we got to find that bad guy. Where is he?")
NSLOCTEXT("[05E61EAF43335DD037F8E3A956D5F63F]", "D20EBC3C4D54AC673C1A4C9040BE8732", "He\'s next door. I\'ll unlock the seal at the door.")
NSLOCTEXT("[05E61EAF43335DD037F8E3A956D5F63F]", "041B7A6248AE8CB53AA7D9889113E7EE", "So please go and see what you can do.")
NSLOCTEXT("[05E61EAF43335DD037F8E3A956D5F63F]", "C903E97A462C6C4E3F7C24A93AECBF61", "I see. Alright, I\'ll help you!")
